  &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/disqus/DISQUS-API-Recipes/blob/master/snippets/js/disqus-reset/disqus_reset.html&quot;&gt; An example DISQUS.reset recipe&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

